data.description: Beautiful four-bedroom Colonial nestled in the heart of Sound Beach boasts open-floor plan living room with wood-burning fireplace and updated kitchen with Quartz countertops. Formal Dining Room with sliders opening up to the rear deck which is perfect for entertaining. Large family room/den, and first-floor bedroom/office. Full bath on first floor. Cathedral-ceiling entryway with sweeping staircase leading to the primary bedroom plus two secondary bedrooms and full bath. Large full-unfinished basement with tons of potential to make it your own. Laundry and utilities. Close proximity to Stony Brook University, shopping and beaches. Move-in ready!
